Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.17,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:46.14,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你的气味 令人发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:50.14,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}真夜中醒来
